{"data":[{"date":"09:04 22/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Bahrain","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-da-biet-ro-suc-manh-cua-bahrain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd L\u01b0u Danh Minh th\u00ec HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i mai 23/8.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Olympic Bahrain&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Bahrain, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng E. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i b\u1edfi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng L\u01b0u Danh Minh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh BHL \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Park Hang Seo\" title=\"Park Hang Seo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/viet-nam-vuot-nhat-ban-dau-an-thay-park.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV&nbsp;Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho v\u00f2ng 1/8, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed hai tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd L\u01b0u Danh Minh v\u00e0 Lee Young Sub \u0111i h\u01a1n 80 km \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Olympic Bahrain v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 15/8 v\u1eeba qua. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-6. D\u1ef1a tr\u00ean b\u0103ng ghi h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00ecn ra nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Bahrain. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, Bahrain g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u01a1i nhanh, m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 pressing n\u1eeda s\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Bahrain ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1 thua t\u1edbi 0-6 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang. Theo g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, Bahrain ch\u01a1i h\u01a1i \u0111\u01a1n \u0111i\u1ec7u, ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i tr\u1ed9i \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y&rdquo;, \u00f4ng L\u01b0u Danh Minh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean Bongdaplus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qua \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ecb tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd n\u00e0y c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng L\u01b0u Danh Minh cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: &ldquo;\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1 n\u00e0y tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 non kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 gi\u1ecfi trong vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eeba qua c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung cao \u0111\u1ed9, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Bahrain&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i mai 23/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-gioi-chuyen-mon-chi-trich-sau-tran-gap-nhat-ban-hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-168-195010.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/bi-gioi-chuyen-mon-chi-trich-sau-tran-gap-nhat-ban-hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-gioi-chuyen-mon-chi-trich-sau-tran-gap-nhat-ban-hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-168-195010.html\">B\u1ecb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chi\u1ec1u 21/8, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194961.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/vff5479-15341729950901227889727.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194961.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/viet-nam-vuot-nhat-ban-dau-an-thay-park-168-194864.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/viet-nam-vuot-nhat-ban-dau-an-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/viet-nam-vuot-nhat-ban-dau-an-thay-park-168-194864.html\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n th\u1ea7y Park</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u 19/8 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i. Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n b\u1ed9...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5766","checkdouble":"195030"},{"date":"09:37 22/08","title":"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/6/hlv-le-thuy-hai-du-doan-thanh-tich-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c khi to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i AS h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i AS h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-du-doan-thanh-tich-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-tai-AS-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;Bahrain ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 &ldquo;\u0103n hi\u1ebfp&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1eady. \u00cdt nhi\u1ec1u, n\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 ba \u1edf m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u1ecd y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n, k\u00e9m h\u01a1n m\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t v\u1ecdng cao nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng 1/8 th\u00f4i, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang t\u00f4i, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng 1/8 th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau xa h\u01a1n cho \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD n\u0103m nay. Qua v\u00f2ng 1/8 t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft th\u00ec U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Th\u1eadt may \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i tr\u1ed9i. Palestine kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, trong khi Syria d\u00f9 g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1edbn lao l\u00e0 \u0111i t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u00e1c em \u0111ang c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1t v\u1ecdng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 l\u00e0m cho con ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 U23 Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8 tr\u00ean SV\u0110 Patriot Candrabhaga t\u1ea1i Bekasi.&nbsp;V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p Palestine/Syria. Tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 27/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-da-biet-ro-suc-manh-cua-bahrain-168-195030.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-da-biet-ro-suc-manh-cua-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-da-biet-ro-suc-manh-cua-bahrain-168-195030.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Bahrain</span><br>\r\nTheo chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd L\u01b0u Danh Minh th\u00ec HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i mai 23/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-toan-tay-a-khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan-168-194952.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-du-doan-thanh-tich-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-tai-AS-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-toan-tay-a-khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan-168-194952.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee5ng to\u00e0n T\u00e2y \u00c1: Khi t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u1ed9t nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p to\u00e0n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1m may cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5765","checkdouble":"195049"},{"date":"11:15 22/08","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Bahrain: K\u1ebb th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/21/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Bahrain ch\u1ec9 mang theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U21 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>Mohammed Al-Hardan &ndash; ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Bahrain</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Bahrain tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 tr\u1ebb, \u0111a ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U21. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i, 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00e1 bi\u1ec7t c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 18 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 Bahrain c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y b\u1edfi h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, qua \u0111\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2020 v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 Olympic Tokyo 2020.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng b\u1edfi tham v\u1ecdng n\u00e0y m\u00e0 Olympic Bahrain \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tuy v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p coi th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi trong tay h\u1ecd \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mohamed Al-Hardan, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c gia T\u00e2y \u00c1 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mohammed Al-Hardan  K\u1ebb th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mohammed Al-Hardan  K\u1ebb th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Olympic-Viet-Nam-dung-toan-Tay-A-Khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Mohammed Al-Hardan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mohammed Al-Hardan sinh n\u0103m 1997. L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t Bahrain l\u00e0 Al-Muharraq t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf, Al-Hardan \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed3ng trang l\u1ee9a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m 18 tu\u1ed5i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Al-Muharraq v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bahraini King's Cup ngay m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. C\u0169ng trong n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, Al-Hardan&nbsp;tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n U19 Bahrain tham d\u1ef1 VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra ngay t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Mohammed Al-Hardan l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. V\u1edbi nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 dao c\u1ea1o, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi U19 Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap U19 Bahrain gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng A.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi Mohammed Al-Hardan v\u00e0 \u0110T U19 Bahrain t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Mohammed Al-Hardan l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t do \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2. Thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng quan tr\u1ecdng, U19 Bahrain \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Tr\u1ea7n Th\u00e0nh \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 72 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup sau gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m bu\u1ed3n nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Mohammed Al-Hardan v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. V\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea7n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 c\u0169 hai n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-khi-asiad-bay-gio-moi-thuc-su-bat-dau-168-194951.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-khi-asiad-bay-gio-moi-thuc-su-bat-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-khi-asiad-bay-gio-moi-thuc-su-bat-dau-168-194951.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain: Khi ASIAD b\u00e2y gi\u1edd m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u</span><br>\r\nOlympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Song tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo b\u1edfi s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p &lsquo;b\u1ecf qu\u00ean&rsquo; Al-Hardan<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Bahrain, Mohammed Al-Hardan c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Al-Hardan l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Bahrain \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i khi \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB Vejle Boldklub, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i tr\u1eddi \u00c2u, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Al-Hardan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, Mohammad Al-Hardan \u0111ang d\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eeba c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u00e2ng cao h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Al-Hardan, ngay c\u1ea3 BHL CLB Vejle Boldklub c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bahrain. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Jacob Kruger cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Al-Hardan ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t nhanh t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u1eadu ta \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn v\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh trong \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y \u1edf ch\u00e0ng trai n\u00e0y ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu ta \u0111\u1ebfn 2020&quot;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam tap nhe truoc tran dau voi Nhat Ban chieu 19/8\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n chi\u1ec1u 19/8\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p &lsquo;b\u1ecf qu\u00ean&rsquo; Al-Hardan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf khi m\u00e0 Al-Hardan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Olympic Malaysia \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Bahrain l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n Al-Hardan c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i anh n\u0103m x\u01b0a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao l\u00ean t\u1edbi 1m83 c\u00f9ng ngu\u1ed3n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o, Al-Hardan ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nguy hi\u1ec3m m\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i &lsquo;ch\u0103m s\u00f3c&rsquo; r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu b\u1ecf s\u00f3t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eaft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i ra nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n l\u00fac n\u00e0y Al-Hardan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 anh t\u1eebng vay b\u1edfi l\u1ee9a Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh n\u0103m x\u01b0a. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Bahrain c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Al-Hardan v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y mai 23/8. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean c\u00e1c k\u00eanh s\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a VOV v\u00e0 VTC. Ngo\u00e0i ra NHM c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng Internet th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">https://beta.vtcnow.vn/kenh/vtc3<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">https://vtc.gov.vn/kenh/vtc3<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-toan-tay-a-khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan-168-194952.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-du-doan-thanh-tich-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-tai-AS-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-toan-tay-a-khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan-168-194952.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee5ng to\u00e0n T\u00e2y \u00c1: Khi t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u1ed9t nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p to\u00e0n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1m may cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span>Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5764","checkdouble":"195054"},{"date":"09:19 22/08","title":"PSG \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft sao tr\u1ebb Brazil tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/22/psg-muon-mua-wesley.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Wesley c\u1ee7a Club Brugge. T\u1edd Le10Sport m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u00f2n nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Wesley n\u1ed5i l\u00ean t\u1ea1i Club Brugge</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWesley Moraes \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i CLB Itabuna qu\u00ea nh\u00e0. \u0110\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2015, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y sang ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ch\u01a1i cho Trencin c\u1ee7a Slovakia. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t, Wesley \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Club Brugge \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft v\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngay \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2016.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i CLB c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 t\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. Sau 71 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y, Wesley ghi t\u1edbi 21 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Wesley c\u1ee7a Club Brugge h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Wesley c\u1ee7a Club Brugge h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/psg-muon-mua-wesley.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Wesley c\u1ee7a Club Brugge</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRi\u00eang m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19, Wesley ghi 3 b\u00e0n trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Club Brugge. \u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i, anh ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 172 ph\u00fat, trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee9 57 ph\u00fat l\u1ea1i ghi 1 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>PSG mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Wesley</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nParis Saint-Germain \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed trinh s\u00e1t vi\u00ean t\u1edbi B\u1ec9 theo d\u00f5i phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Wesley. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Nice l\u00e0 CLB kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Mario Balotelli ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n v\u1edbi PSG, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng cho Edinson Cavani. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8. V\u1edbi t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 3 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1eb1ng Cavani s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i PSG hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWesley l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Cavani. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t (cao 1m92) v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh trong kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn song c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng PSG tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chot-gia-ban-rakitic-cho-psg-180-194989.html\">Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Rakitic cho PSG?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nang-gia-hoi-mua-cavani-len-63-trieu-bang-180-194880.html\">Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/co-doi-bong-chi-100-trieu-bang-mua-christian-eriksen-172-194466.html\">C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Christian Eriksen</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-va-barca-nhan-tin-vui-vu-rabiot-180-194392.html\">Real v\u00e0 Barca nh\u1eadn tin vui v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-rabiot-cua-psg-180-194389.html\">Real l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cu\u1ed7m m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5763","checkdouble":"195039"},{"date":"11:18 22/08","title":"\"Messi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Argentina l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o n\u1eefa\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/messi-se-khong-con-khoac-ao-dt-argentina-lan-nao-nua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 k\u1ebft th\u00fac trong th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Lionel Messi t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia Argentina.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMessi v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1eb9n ng\u00e0y t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, \u0110T Argentina \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Jorge Sampaoli b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng Lionel Scaloni \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 li\u1ec7u Messi c\u00f3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Albiceleste s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u1edbi Guatemala v\u00e0 Colombia. Nh\u01b0ng trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Scaloni, c\u00e1i t\u00ean Leo Messi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Argentina cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Messi v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp anh \u1ea5y trong 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Th\u00e0nh th\u1ef1c m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft vai tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Messi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, h\u00e3y ch\u1edd xem nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lionel Messi t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia Argentina\" title=\"Messi that vong Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/messi-se-khong-con-khoac-ao-dt-argentina-lan-nao-nua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lionel Messi t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Messi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f9ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi nhau. Messi s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf l\u1ea7n tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, h\u00e3y ch\u1edd xem. D\u00f9 sao, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 v\u1edbi nghi ng\u1edd Lionel Messi t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia Argentina, nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1u binh nh\u01b0 Sergio Aguero, Nicolas Otamendi, Angel Di Maria v\u00e0 Gonzalo Higuain c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ecb qu\u00ean l\u00e3ng nh\u01b0 Mauro Icardi, hay nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi Lautaro Martinez v\u00e0 Giovanni Simeone \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lionel-messi-giup-barca-chien-thang-nguoi-argentina-lieu-co-chanh-long-180-194790.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/lionel-messi-giup-barca-chien-thang-nguoi-argentina-lieu-co-chanh-long.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lionel-messi-giup-barca-chien-thang-nguoi-argentina-lieu-co-chanh-long-180-194790.html\">Lionel Messi gi\u00fap Barca chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 ch\u1ea1nh l\u00f2ng?</span><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina h\u1eb3n s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1nh l\u00f2ng khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cho Barca. N\u1ebfu anh \u0111\u00e1 hay nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u1edf World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/lich-thi-dau/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga-181-194781.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/lich-thi-dau/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga-181-194781.html\">Lionel Messi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Alaves, Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap Barcelona gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u1eadp n\u00ean c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 6.000 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho La...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5762","checkdouble":"195045"},{"date":"10:37 22/08","title":"AC Milan gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao PSG v\u1edbi Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/ac-milan-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-rabiot-voi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>AC Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Barca \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Adrien Rabiot l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Andres Iniesta, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1995. Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Barca \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"AC Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"AC Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/ac-milan-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-rabiot-voi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rabiot</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Sport, PSG \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a ra, song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-chot-gia-mua-adrien-rabiot-180-194994.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Rabiot </span>v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u euro, h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Rabiot v\u1edbi PSG ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Barca tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 50 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. TTCN H\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n g\u1ea7n 10 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa l\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, Barca v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda PSG.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Rabiot \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n tin r\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7\u00a0ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>AC Milan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rabiot</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Barca \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Le10Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Leonardo c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Rabiot v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rabiot cua PSG\" title=\"Rabiot cua PSG\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/real-va-barca-nhan-tin-vui-vu-rabiot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>AC Milan c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Rabiot</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, AC Milan kh\u00f4ng h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2019 khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi PSG \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi Rabiot c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do, nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 AC Milan s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t xu n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5761","checkdouble":"195051"},{"date":"11:01 22/08","title":"Bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Everton th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Kane, Salah gi\u00e0nh gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/bom-tan-cua-everton-thach-thuc-kane-salah-gianh-giay-vang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110ang c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Everton, t\u00e2n binh Richarlison mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League ngay m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRicharlison \u0111\u1eb7t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u1edbn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi HLV Marco Silva. Sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Premier League 2018/19, Richarlison \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ti\u1ebfng vang l\u1edbn khi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng sinh n\u0103m 1997 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, v\u00e0 anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Richarlison cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u00edch nghi v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u01b0a Everton gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 Champions League, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia Brazil.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Richarlison mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League\" title=\"Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/bom-tan-cua-everton-thach-thuc-kane-salah-gianh-giay-vang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Richarlison mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng 20 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Selecao, trong 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1edbi M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 El Salvador. L\u1eddi tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a HLV Tite \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n, nh\u01b0ng Richarlison cho bi\u1ebft, anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee3i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;D\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c hy v\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t cho c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai&rdquo; &ndash; t\u00e2n binh 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Richarlison mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League, anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Salah hay Harry Kane.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ly-do-yerry-mina-khong-toi-man-united-172-194617.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/day-ly-do-yerry-mina-khong-toi-man-united.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ly-do-yerry-mina-khong-toi-man-united-172-194617.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Yerry Mina kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Man United</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Everton v\u1eeba h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 l\u00ed do v\u00ec sao h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park thay v\u00ec Man United.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-kich-no-bom-tan-premier-league-50-trieu-bang-172-191974.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/everton-kich-no-bom-tan-premier-league-50-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-kich-no-bom-tan-premier-league-50-trieu-bang-172-191974.html\">Everton ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Premier League 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5760","checkdouble":"195047"},{"date":"09:44 22/08","title":"Kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, Man City gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft ra sao?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/man-city-tinh-goi-lai-aro-muric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City t\u00ednh g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i Aro Muric thay Claudio Bravo ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i 1 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t Ederson l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady. </h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bravo ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Claudio Bravo \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee9t g\u00e2n Achilles v\u00e0 trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi s\u1ebd bay sang Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea9y HLV Pep Guardiola v\u00e0o b\u00e0i to\u00e1n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00e1 h\u00f3c b\u00faa. \u0110\u1ed9i 1 c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t Ederton l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City t\u00ednh g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i Aro Muric thay Claudio Bravo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City t\u00ednh g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i Aro Muric thay Claudio Bravo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/man-city-tinh-goi-lai-aro-muric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bravo ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea9y Joe Hart v\u00e0 Angus Gunn t\u1edbi Burnley v\u00e0 Southampton. N\u1ebfu gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean hi\u1ec7n tr\u1ea1ng, Man City bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f4n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Ederson.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>G\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i Aro Muric</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City t\u00ednh g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i Aro Muric \u0111ang ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i NAC Breda. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bravo sau cu\u1ed9c x\u00e9t nghi\u1ec7m chi ti\u1ebft \u1edf Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Aro Muric\" title=\"thu mon Aro Muric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/thu-mon-Aro-Muric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Man City t\u00ednh g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i Aro Muric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAro Muric sinh ra \u1edf Zurich, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 nh\u01b0ng l\u1edbn l\u00ean \u1edf Montenegro. Anh gia nh\u1eadp Man City t\u1eeb Grasshoppers v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n cao t\u1edbi 1m98 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 gi\u00e0u tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft NAC Breda tr\u01b0\u1edbc De Graafschap, Muric \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 Lan gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Man City, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 19 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng 11 l\u1ea7n sau 12 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a y\u00ean t\u00e2m, Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u01a1n xin vi\u1ec7n binh l\u00ean ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c Premier League. Chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c CLB h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb kh\u00f3a l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n nay c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-phu-nhan-mua-cillessen-vao-thang-1-172-195029.html\">Man City ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua sao Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-sap-mua-duoc-gavin-bazunu-172-195006.html\">Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tu\u1ed5i teen</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jason-denayer-sap-roi-man-city-172-194995.html\">B\u1ea1n c\u0169 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-john-stones-172-194898.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-ruben-neves-vao-thang-1-172-194884.html\">Man City chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ruben Neves v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5759","checkdouble":"195048"},{"date":"10:48 22/08","title":"B\u1ecb Mourinho \u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Smalling n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/27/bi-mourinho-day-ai-tren-bang-ghe-du-bi-smalling-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chris Smalling n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh thay v\u00ec ra \u0111i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Smalling b\u1ecb Mourinho b\u1ecf r\u01a1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Chris Smalling l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, Chris Smalling n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, Chris Smalling n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Lien-tuc-ngoi-du-bi,-Chris-Smalling-noi-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng Smalling kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh, nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n sung s\u1ee9c s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Song th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Victor Lindelof v\u00e0 Eric Bailly. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng Smalling mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Italia v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u sao Fulham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Smalling l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chris Smalling n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh thay v\u00ec ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Smalling vs Tottenham\" title=\"Smalling vs Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/23/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-18,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng khi t\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. HLV c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n t\u00f4i ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. T\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Lindelof v\u00e0 Bailly ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn thua Brighton \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Smalling s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tottenham \u1edf v\u00f2ng 3. Hi\u1ec7n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang x\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa BXH Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5758","checkdouble":"195052"},{"date":"11:29 22/08","title":"Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: M.U c\u1ea7n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho v\u00e0 m\u1eddi Zidane thay th\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/quan-diem-mu-can-sa-thai-mourinho-va-moi-zidane-thay-the.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0nh cho Jose Mourinho t\u1ea1i Man United \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eafp h\u1ebft! Nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng xoay c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t\u201d t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t CLB lu\u00f4n nhu\u1ed1m m\u00e0u bi th\u01b0\u01a1ng. M.U c\u1ea7n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho v\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Zinedine Zidane.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U c\u1ea7n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi kh\u1edfi nghi\u1ec7p HLV t\u1edbi nay, <u>\u0111i\u1ec7p kh\u00fac 2 n\u0103m vui, 1 n\u0103m bu\u1ed3n c\u1ee9 l\u1eb7p \u0111i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Jose Mourinho</u>. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i, ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a &ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t&rdquo; trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh hi\u1ec7n nay nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu khi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi M.U c\u1ea7n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n kh\u1eafp m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i. Bongda24h.vn c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Mourinho. Nh\u1eefng c\u01a1n d\u1eb1n v\u1eb7t v\u00ec th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 v\u1edbi Mou \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ed3n c\u00e0o nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 quen v\u1edbi n\u00f3 t\u1eeb Real Madrid, Chelsea v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU c\u1ea7n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho v\u00e0 thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng Zidane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU c\u1ea7n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho v\u00e0 thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng Zidane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/MU-can-sa-thai-Mourinho-va-thay-the-bang-Zidane-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho \u0111ang \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u1ebft xe \u0111\u1ed5 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Mourinho s\u1ebd xoay chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf, t\u1eeb t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng <em>d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c bi th\u1ea3m</em> \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u00f4ng l\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton ng\u00e0y ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt cho th\u1ea5y <strong>Premier League nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed3ng th\u1ee7y \u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f2n \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n M.U trong tay Mou ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 con thuy\u1ec1n nh\u1ecf b\u00e9</strong>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Mourinho t\u1ea1i M.U, n\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n tay tr\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ebfn m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ecb qu\u1ef7 \u00e1m n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng ai ngh\u0129 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ch\u00e8o l\u00e1i. Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 <u>chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n cho vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Mou b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1 kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Old Trafford</u>. Nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u1ec7t k\u00ea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neu gay su voi Ed Woodward, Jose Mourinho se la nguoi chiu thiet.\" title=\"N\u1ebfu g\u00e2y s\u1ef1 v\u1edbi Ed Woodward, Jose Mourinho s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu thi\u1ec7t.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/mourinho-9.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i gh\u1ebf HLV&nbsp;tr\u01b0\u1edfng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean Mauricio Pochettino, Max Allegri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid, <u>Zinedine Zidane m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t</u>. So v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c, <em>Zizou hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a Mourinho h\u01a1n ai h\u1ebft</em> b\u1edfi m\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4i, \u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00f9ng Real tr\u1ea3i qua t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 M.U hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn ra Real, m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf La Liga v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Zidane lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Los Blancos gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zidane-duoc-ung-ho-thay-the-mourinho-o-man-utd-172-195020.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/zidane-duoc-ung-ho-thay-the-mourinho-o-man-utd.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zidane-duoc-ung-ho-thay-the-mourinho-o-man-utd-172-195020.html\">Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 thay th\u1ebf Mourinho \u1edf Man Utd</span><br>\r\n<span>C\u1ef1u Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf Lee Sharpe kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Jose Mourinho s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2018 v\u00e0 Zinedine Zidane l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>S\u1ef1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a M.U th\u1eddi Mourinho th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</strong>. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u1ed9ng 2 tr\u1eadn thi\u1ebfu thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i Premier League l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u00edt \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u1eeb n\u1eeda sau m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League, B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea1n ki\u1ec7t d\u1ea7n sinh kh\u00ed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng sau \u0111\u00eam Old Trafford \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 (thua Sevilla 1-2), <u>nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 M.U \u0111\u00e3 quay l\u01b0ng v\u1edbi Mourinho</u>. C\u00e1c Manucians ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng in \u0111\u1eadm suy ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 khi M.U gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 Premier League v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap FA, C\u0110V c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00ec Mourinho. V\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e2m v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng, xung quanh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c tranh lu\u1eadn ai s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i l\u00ean gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho va Zidane\" title=\"Mourinho va Zidane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/Mourinho-va-Zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>M.U c\u1ea7n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nZidane l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPochettino l\u00e0 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c l\u00f4i k\u00e9o chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Tottenham, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf v\u1edbi M.U v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. C\u00f2n Allegri, n\u1ebfu l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ng\u1ecf l\u1eddi v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Allegri c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo nh\u1eb1m ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u1ee7a Bianconeri. M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u00f4ng kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng r\u1eddi qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Italia \u0111i theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-khong-ai-con-du-kien-nhan-voi-mourinho-nua-roi-172-195041.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/huyen-thoai-mu-khong-ai-con-du-kien-nhan-voi-mourinho-nua-roi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-khong-ai-con-du-kien-nhan-voi-mourinho-nua-roi-172-195041.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU: Kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i</span><br>\r\n<span>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Viv Anderson cho r\u1eb1ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho \u1edf Man United khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi \u00f4ng.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 <strong>Zidane nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee9u c\u00e1nh cho M.U</strong> v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec &ldquo;gai trong m\u1eaft&rdquo; Mourinho. Hi\u1ec7n Zizou \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay th\u1ebf Mou b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. Kinh nghi\u1ec7m &ldquo;ch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y&rdquo; t\u1ea1i Real h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00f4ng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u1ed1t b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i Old Trafford l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<u>Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 &ldquo;Mr. Ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o&rdquo; cho M.U</u>. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m y\u00ean l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a HLV 46 tu\u1ed5i. Qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 t\u1ea1i Real ch\u1ec9 ra Zidane \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t kh\u00e2u khu\u1ebfch \u0111\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t gi\u00fap \u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u bao g\u1ed3m 3 Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ai \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Mourinho t\u1ea1i M.U l\u00fac n\u00e0y? Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Anthony Martial. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u xem Zidane nh\u01b0 th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb thu\u1edf nh\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zidane\" title=\"Zidane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/MU-sa-thai-Jose-Mourinho-bo-nhiem-Zinedine-Zidane--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zidane \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ch\u00e8o l\u00e1i M.U v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua gian kh\u00f3</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nZidane ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1i M.U. \u00d4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t HLV ph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a M.U, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ngh\u0129 ngay t\u1edbi th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00ed th\u1ebf th\u1eddi Sir Alex Ferguson. M\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Zidane l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n 3 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Zidane, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng minh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i Real Madrid. S\u1ee9c quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 c\u1ee7a Premier League r\u1ed3i cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ed v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Pep Guardiola, Jurgen Klopp, Pochettino hay Maurizio Sarri&hellip; l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Zidane. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn: M\u1ed9t HLV \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 3 danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League v\u00e0 1 La Liga kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 nh\u1edd may m\u1eafn. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Zidane c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft gian kh\u00f3 \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p nh\u01b0 Real Madrid, kh\u00f4ng l\u00fd g\u00ec \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u1edbt con t\u00e0u \u0111ang b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1n tr\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"nhung danh hieu Zidane va Real\" title=\"nhung danh hieu Zidane va Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/Goc-Real-Tam-biet-Zizou,-Mr-Hoan-hao-cua-chung-toi!-hinh-anh-4.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-khien-mu-guc-nga-truoc-brighton-172-194858.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194855.html\">M.U phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Jose Mourinho: Con thuy\u1ec1n m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\">Man Utd thua th\u1ea3m: \u0110\u00fang r\u1ed3i Jose, ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5757","checkdouble":"195055"},{"date":"11:57 22/08","title":"\u0110\u1eb1ng sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton: S\u1ef1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/dang-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-mu-truoc-brighton-su-sup-do-cua-hang-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nghi ng\u1edd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y M.U ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1eeb m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t bom x\u1ecbt&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb x\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn nay, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi, l\u1ea5y ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u00e0m c\u01a1 s\u1edf cho th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi, c\u1ea3 Chelsea l\u1eabn Inter Milan \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y ti\u1ebfng vang l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u b\u1eb1ng phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 khi HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2016, \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd th\u1eafp l\u1ea1i \u00e1nh h\u00e0o quang \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eaft n\u01a1i Nh\u00e0 h\u00e1t. C\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, r\u1eb1ng CLB l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa h\u1ed3i sinh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1ng tro t\u00e0n. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, v\u1edbi 3 danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em v\u1ec1. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 t\u1ea1i Premier League l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a ti\u1ebfp theo, Jose Mourinho th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi, khi M.U l\u00e0 1 trong 2 CLB gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i Premier League. H\u1ecd ghi b\u00e0n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u00edt th\u1ee9 2, nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y &ndash; d\u00f9 M.U tr\u1eafng tay to\u00e0n t\u1eadp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec tr\u1ea3i qua trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 nghi ng\u1edd t\u0103ng cao. H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i lo c\u1ee7a Mourinho, d\u00f9 n\u0103m n\u00e0o \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi. <strong>&ldquo;\u0110\u00f4i b\u1ea1n ch\u1eadm ti\u1ebfn&rdquo;</strong> Phil Jones &ndash; Chris Smalling \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng Ferdinand, Vidic m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Nh\u00e0 h\u00e1t, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f3. Jones d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian \u1edf b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f2n Smalling tr\u1eadn hay \u00edt h\u01a1n tr\u1eadn d\u1edf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 S\u1ef1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"MU ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 S\u1ef1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/MU-phong-ngu-rat-te-Su-sup-do-bat-dau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t ch\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u00e0i to\u00e1n ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u1edf phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u00f2n Lindelof \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, khi ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Leicester City kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Trong b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 1-2 c\u1ee7a The Foxes, c\u1ea3 David De Gea l\u1eabn Eric Bailly \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ecn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u1eeda s\u00fat n\u1eeda chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1ec3 Jamie Vardy d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo c\u00f2n t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, khi M.U th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n b\u1edfi Brighton. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Murray li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t Lindelof, c\u00f2n Bailly c\u0169ng ch\u1eedng kh\u00e1 h\u01a1n khi m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chris Hughton. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh c\u00f2n cho r\u1eb1ng, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Eric Bailly g\u00e2y nguy hi\u1ec3m cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7: S\u1ef1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"MU th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/nhm-mu-phan-ung-cuc-soc-sau-tran-thua-brighton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn trong ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1eeda t\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U li\u00ean h\u1ec7, v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd thu v\u1ec1 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng tr\u00f2n tr\u0129nh. Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 r\u00f5 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 Mourinho mu\u1ed1n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c, m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Nh\u1eefng Jerome Boateng, Toby Alderweireld \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7, r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 Yerry Mina, Harry Maguire \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, d\u00f9 Mourinho v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e8m mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a PCT ki\u00eam G\u0110\u0110H Ed Woodward, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n Mourinho trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. V\u00e0 khi nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, Woodward \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng y\u00eau s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. M.U ch\u01b0a m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7: S\u1ef1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Mourinho v\u00e0 Ed Woodward\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Goc-nhin-Mourinho-can-phai-lac-quan-hon-ve-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7, nh\u01b0ng Ed Woodward kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n chi ti\u1ec1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd, PCT c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111ang nghi ng\u1edd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Mourinho, v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng li\u1ec7u \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9m ti\u1ec1n qua c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 trong nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y? N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u. M\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Mourinho, m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng &ndash; c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man United c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau g\u00ec \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 v\u00e0 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Mourinho. &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u00f3&rdquo; &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi chia s\u1ebb m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ed1t ra khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i trong th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n cho c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Ed Woodward, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang qu\u00e1 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng ti\u1ec1n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb v\u1ee9t \u0111i. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng suy ngh\u0129 n\u00e0y trong \u0111\u1ea7u Ed: <strong>&ldquo;M\u1ed9t HLV s\u1eafp b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i th\u00ec c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n mua s\u1eafm l\u00e0m g\u00ec?&rdquo;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-mu-can-sa-thai-mourinho-va-moi-zidane-thay-the-172-195055.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/quan-diem-mu-can-sa-thai-mourinho-va-moi-zidane-thay-the.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-mu-can-sa-thai-mourinho-va-moi-zidane-thay-the-172-195055.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: M.U c\u1ea7n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho v\u00e0 m\u1eddi Zidane thay th\u1ebf</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian d\u00e0nh cho Jose Mourinho t\u1ea1i Man United \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eafp h\u1ebft! Nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng xoay c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a &ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t&rdquo; t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t CLB lu\u00f4n nhu\u1ed1m...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sieu-co-raiola-chi-trich-scholes-san-sang-dem-pogba-roi-mu-172-194987.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/sieu-co-raiola-chi-trich-scholes-san-sang-dem-pogba-roi-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sieu-co-raiola-chi-trich-scholes-san-sang-dem-pogba-roi-mu-172-194987.html\">Si\u00eau c\u00f2 Raiola ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Scholes, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111em Pogba r\u1eddi M.U</span><br>\r\nN\u1ed9i t\u00ecnh \u1edf M.U v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft lo\u1ea1n, khi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y g\u00e3 b\u00e9o Mino Raiola ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Paul Scholes v\u00ec nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 Pogba.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5756","checkdouble":"195058"},{"date":"07:38 22/08","title":"Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Juventus ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/ronaldo-khong-the-giup-juventus-tiep-tuc-thong-tri-nuoc-y.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Allan c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i Napoli c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Serie A.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau khi chia tay Real Madrid v\u00e0 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh Turin v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Cristiano Ronaldo cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus g\u1eb7p Chievo Verona \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Serie A 2018/19.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00e1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng hay ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Juventus c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Se h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Se h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/ronaldo-khong-the-giup-juventus-tiep-tuc-thong-tri-nuoc-y.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Allan c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i Napoli c\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea1nh mi\u1ec7ng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o CR7 v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Italia. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil: &ldquo;S\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd khi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ee9c h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng cao.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng r\u1ed3i, nh\u01b0ng Ronaldo c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c. Juventus ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Serie A th\u00eam n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e2u.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t s\u00edt sao v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i cho th\u1ea5y Napoli ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 Juventus trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Ronaldo s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 khi Juventus ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Lazio, b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh Napoli trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5755","checkdouble":"195019"},{"date":"08:26 22/08","title":"H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/hang-loat-doi-bong-lon-nhan-don-dau-vu-pjanic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Miralem Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Miralem Pjanic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Miralem Pjanic c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus t\u1eeb Roma v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 32 tri\u1ec7u euro, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Juventus.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Miralem Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Miralem Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/hang-loat-doi-bong-lon-nhan-don-dau-vu-pjanic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n mua Pjanic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i Pjanic ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn 44 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng khi v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Pjanic l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A v\u00e0 C\u00fap QG Italia v\u1edbi Juventus trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-tinh-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-pjanic-180-194470.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Miralem Pjanic</span>, Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City c\u0169ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990. Khi m\u00e0 phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00ec Los Blancos \u0111ang m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u1ef1a trong vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Pjanic.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN nh\u1eafm Miralem Pjanic thay Luka Modric, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i. Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 70 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Juventus nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 Miralem Pjanic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Miralem Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus vs Porto Pjanic\" title=\"Juventus vs Porto Pjanic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/2/23/juventus-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-man-city-voi-gia-50-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Pjanic gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda Juventus x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i, anh s\u1ebd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 6 n\u0103m 2023. \u0110\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pjanic h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Juventus v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Juventus, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Miralem Pjanic l\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd y\u00ean t\u00e2m c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5754","checkdouble":"195028"}]}